flowchart LR
  U[User or environment]

  subgraph RuntimeSystems[Executable agent orchestration runtimes]
    L[01 Loop runtime<br/>canonical state: direct runner state]
    G[02 Graph runtime<br/>canonical state: shared graph state]
    S[03 Sheaf runtime<br/>canonical state: certified global section]
  end

  subgraph IndependentChecks[Independent checks; not orchestrators]
    C[Conformance tests]
    E[Mechanism scorecard]
    D[04 Dominance evaluation]
  end

  U --> L
  U --> G
  U --> S

  L --> LO[Output, effects, trace]
  G --> GO[Output, effects, trace]
  S --> SO[Output, effects, trace]

  LO -. observed .-> C
  GO -. observed .-> C
  SO -. observed .-> C

  LO -. observed .-> E
  GO -. observed .-> E
  SO -. observed .-> E

  L -. comparison class .-> D
  G -. comparison class .-> D
  S -. candidate system .-> D

  D --> R[Source-bound evidence and release archive]
